-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 6

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3

            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 5 ORDER BY v.id

            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 5 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 5 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 12 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 13 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 13 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 13 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 16 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 16 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 3 GROUP BY v.id

            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 13 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 13 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 16 GROUP BY v.id

-- SQL -- SELECT v.id,v.fecha_pago,v.total,v.fecha_compra,v.estatus,p.nombre as producto,CONCAT(c.empresa,' ') as cliente 
            FROM innovasys_general.cat_asignacion as a 
            INNER JOIN  innovasys_car100.tb_carrito as v ON v.id = a.id_carrito
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.tb_clientes as c ON c.id=v.id_cliente
            INNER JOIN innovasys_car100.cat_productos as p ON p.id=v.id_producto
            where p.tipoWeb='VDC'AND a.id_usuario = 16 GROUP BY v.id
